    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, increase the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>diced courgette</strong>, <strong>diced pepper</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cumin seeds</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped garlic</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 6-7 min further or until the vegetables have started to soften</p>",
