    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the vegetables are softening, dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>in 550ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
