    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>tortillas</strong> into triangle shapes (layer them up to speed up the process!)</p><p>Add the <strong>tortilla triangles</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, so the <strong>tortilla triangles </strong>are evenly coated in the oil and put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 6-8 min or until golden and crisp – these are your<strong> tortilla chips</strong></p>",
